snippet.title: Wanna LAUGH? BIRDS will NOT DISAPPOINT YOU! - Funniest BIRD VIDEOS
snippet.description:
Birds can be extremely funny! Birds are so hilarious and never fail to make us laugh! These bird videos are the hardest try not to laugh challenge! Just look how all these parrots, chickens, smaller birds,... behave, play, fail, make funny sounds, talk, react to different things,... So ridiculous, funny and cute! What is your favorite clip? :) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!
